Again Recon grabbed both blades and held onto them very tightly. "Liar, the 
maximal matrix is just a story made up by the quintessons. They fooled you 
the same as they fooled galvatron by telling him there was a decepticon 
matrix of leadership. I was lucky enough to have a piece of the autobot 
matrix to bond with my own spark, it gives me strength. The strength I need 
to take down Aerotaur. If he were a normal enemy it would be one thing. But 
he claimed his body was made by the devil himself. And me being the 
"religious looney" that I am, I must defeat him," Recon tells him.
